reviewText: Very good film which looks at the American Indian with warmth and  compassion. They have a real dignity which is rare in the film of this period. Quinn is terrific and so is DeMille. DVD arrived in time. The film should be restored
My husband has a bit part in this movie... he was 12 yrs old at the time... and has never seen the movie.  This was such a treat for him.  It arrived in perfect condition.  love it!
